I"Ø(<h1 id="objective">Objective</h1>
<p>By using P-Splines (Penalized Smoothing Splines) to draw a smooth line on two dimensional scatter plot on R.</p>

<h1 id="code-examples">Code Examples</h1>

<h3 id="sample-code-from-package-pspline">Sample code from <a href="https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/pspline/pspline.pdf">Package â€˜psplineâ€™</a></h3>

